title: 039 - John Branyan - Aliens, Beards and Nanapalooza
description:

Freight wants a flashlight that you can deep fry. Gonzo becomes a pirate. And the gang gets a phone call from Caleb’s beard.Also on this episode: Tom Cruise is an alien, and other conspiracy theories. John list his favorite horror movies.
